              rdfs:comment "Sub-clase de pokemon que representa un Pokémon de tipo fuego."@es .


###  https://w3id.org/doisr/PokemonOntologyG2#PokemonHada
:PokemonHada rdf:type owl:Class ;
             owl:equivalentClass [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
